                    	<note xml:id="n_remarks" type="remarks">
                    	    
                                    
<p>The envelope has been preserved. Stamp: 15 centimes. The postmark on the front is illegible, apart from ‘PARIS – R <hi rend="italics">[xx]</hi> TTON’. The address reads: ‘Monsieur V.W. van Gogh / chez Monsieur le Dr Peyron / <hi rend="italics">S</hi>t <hi rend="italics">Remy en Provence</hi> / Bouches du Rhône’.</p>
                                    
                                
                    	</note>
                    
                </listAnnotation>
