                </listAnnotation>
                <listAnnotation xml:lang="en" type="notes">
                    
                        <note n="1" xml:id="note-t-1">
                            

<p>These names had been chosen months before. <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#_416">Jo</rs> had already written about the name Vincent at the end of June (<ref target="let786.xml#n-1">see letter 786, n. 1</ref>). The second Christian name had been decided as early as September 1889 (FR b2907 and b2901).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                            

                        
                    
